ygData.messageBody:
For me it depended upon where i was hunting the skels.
∩┐╜
For the roamers I would get darkness to stick, send in pet, then boil blood,
heart flutter, fear as needed.∩┐╜ If darkness didn't stick, it hurt a bit, but
I never died.
∩┐╜
Pulling from the undead rings, i would soothe the dead as needed and pull
with a very small damage spell or siphon strength to bring it over to me,
wait till pet taunts off skel before casting anymore spells or even meleeing
and then start stacking once the pet had the skels full attention.∩┐╜ Siphon
strength worked good for me, it seemed like it took a big chunk of damage
out the skels arsenal
∩┐╜
Vanelin Blackheart
35th DE Nec
